    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >再玩一场有趣的高尔夫吧！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/9eaf5fddc8fc0ae39c754d83e96bbe22.poster.avif?t=1739647965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/9eaf5fddc8fc0ae39c754d83e96bbe22.webm?t=1739647965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/9eaf5fddc8fc0ae39c754d83e96bbe22.mp4?t=1739647965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好迎接超过 50 万次下载的热门续作了吗？<br><br>《口袋迷你高尔夫 2》 将为你带来数小时简单却令人上瘾的游戏体验，无论是独自一人还是与朋友一起！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富关卡，挑战不断！</h2><br>探索多个充满生机的迷你世界！游戏包含4个美妙的迷你世界和100个独特的关卡，色彩缤纷的海洋景观、疯狂的实验室、秘密花园、玩具店——全部都去逛逛，收集宝石来购买新皮肤、搞怪音效和酷炫特效！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样游戏模式，欢乐不断！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/0fb1e31e8a3d4060d15ac639c9179beb.poster.avif?t=1739647965\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/0fb1e31e8a3d4060d15ac639c9179beb.webm?t=1739647965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285980/extras/0fb1e31e8a3d4060d15ac639c9179beb.mp4?t=1739647965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏提供5种模式：战役、挑战、试炼、竞速和宝石猎手。每种模式都有独特的玩法和挑战，确保你永远不会感到无聊！<br><br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4个奇妙的口袋世界，拥有100个独特关卡<br></li><li>陷阱、传送门、发射器、可收集的宝石和道具……应有尽有！<br></li><li>许多可解锁的自定义选项，例如放屁声、彩色球或幽灵轨迹，以及大量奖杯等你来拿！<br></li><li>5 种游戏模式：战斗、挑战、试炼、竞速还有宝石狩猎！</li></ul>",
